  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm the safety and effectiveness of the CardioFocus
      Endoscopic Ablation System with Adaptive Contact in the treatment of atrial fibrillation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
